        {
            "title": "尖沙咀的士猛撞安全島燈柱 司機胸口痛送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"的士撞塌路中燈柱，一人輕傷。fb馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2f2af07712c46b257b0183f324f87b36/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041814200117328.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">的士撞塌路中燈柱，一人輕傷。fb馬路的事 (即時交通資訊台)</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（18日）中午12時43分，一部的士駛至尖沙咀梳士巴利道太空館對開期間，突失控猛撞路中安全島的燈柱，燈柱被撞至傾斜，碎片甩脫。的士司機報稱頸及心口痛，送院敷治。警方正調查意外原因。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064616/即時-港聞-尖沙咀的士猛撞安全島燈柱-司機胸口痛送院",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-18 14:31:26",
