        {
            "title": "Netflix首季盈利升24%勝預期 首次未披露客戶變動數據",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Netflix首季盈利升24%勝預期 首次未披露客戶變動數據\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/df8549e00047b5a5671196b4f4259a9c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041814153360716.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Netflix首季盈利升24%勝預期 首次未披露客戶變動數據</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>網上串流平台Netflix（美：NFLX）公布，截止3月底止的季度，純利按年上升近兩成四，賺28.9億美元。每股攤薄盈利6.61美元，高於市場預期的5.71美元。因會員數量增長和定價上漲，期內收入按年增長13%至105億美元，符預期。\n\n</p>\n<p>消息刺激Netflix周四市後延長交易時段，股價升逾2%，全日收市升1.2%，收報973.03美元。\n\n</p>\n<p>Netflix稱，訂閱和廣告收入略高於預期，主要是受惠於今年1月全面上調價格。營業利潤率由去年同期28%上升至32%，預期第二季為33%。\n\n</p>\n<p>至於收入和利潤增長前景依然穩健，Netflix預計第二季收入增長將增長15%至110.4億美元，並維持全年收入預期不變，料介乎435億美元至445億美元，營業利益率為29%。\n\n</p>\n<p>值得一提的是，本季是Netflix首次在業績中未有披露新增或流失客戶數據，集團指希望投資者專注於評估公司的收入及其他財務數據。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3441598/\">Netflix重磅劇《混沌少年時》「一鏡到底」背後關鍵 來自DJI大疆攝影機 涉4大黑科技優勢</a><br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064614/即時-財經-Netflix首季盈利升24-勝預期-首次未披露客戶變動數據",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-18 14:31:27",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西甲│傳安察洛堤月尾西班牙盃決賽後離開皇馬 轉教巴西帶隊踢世盃外",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"傳安察洛堤月尾西班牙盃決賽後離開皇馬。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/cdd2aa5d0398a0a99d731cb24c99d2ec/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041812212790626.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">傳安察洛堤月尾西班牙盃決賽後離開皇馬。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英國《天空體育》周四報導，皇家馬德里教練安察洛堤大有機會在4月26日的西班牙盃決賽後，與球會協商離隊，然後上任成為巴西國家隊教練。消息人士透露巴西足總方面希望這位意大利名帥盡快上任，領軍在6月出戰世界盃外圍賽。\n\n</p><h2>皇馬球員不再信任安察洛堤</h2>\n<p>皇馬今季成績未如人意，剛周中歐聯8強次回合不敵阿仙奴，被後者雙殺出局，教練安察洛堤的帥位進一步受壓，他賽後受訪時亦直言不知道自己的命運如何。西班牙媒體《Relevo》引述消息人士指，皇馬戰將包括多位資深球員，已向球會主席佩雷斯表示不再信任安察洛堤，認為他的戰術、踢法向布陣已跟不上潮流，希望球會辭退他。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"傳皇馬教練安察洛堤在月尾的西班牙盃決賽後離隊。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0042f7aba8e5051007fe5f1681399a0/2025-04/1_39.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        傳皇馬教練安察洛堤在月尾的西班牙盃決賽後離隊。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安察洛堤今季一直備受壓力。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7f0830d8cd322dc6e4071c2afc259c7f/2025-04/2_25.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安察洛堤今季一直備受壓力。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安察洛堤下一站有望接手巴西國家隊。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3799c332bbd18105413d293537197a28/2025-04/3_38.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安察洛堤下一站有望接手巴西國家隊。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"有傳皇馬球員已不再信任安察洛堤。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/18a05c2499d432a3a74f70ec9a2aabdf/2025-04/4_41.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有傳皇馬球員已不再信任安察洛堤。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇耿球員認為安帥的戰術已跟不上潮流。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27f36d05b75f206e1b96df306ad5863d/2025-04/5_33.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇耿球員認為安帥的戰術已跟不上潮流。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>傳西班牙盃決賽後離隊</h2>\n<p>皇馬本身不想在賽季中途換人，但英國《每日郵報》就透露，近年成績差勁的巴西國家隊再次向這位意大利名帥發起邀請，希望他加入球隊在6月領軍出戰2場世界盃南美洲區外圍賽，想此子盡快加盟。消息人士指，經過協商後，安帥將會在本月26日領軍在西班牙盃決賽鬥巴塞隆拿，完賽後就會離隊，到巴西展開執教生涯新一頁。\n\n</p>\n<p>銀河艦隊會另覓看守教練，其中的選項包括提升安帥兒子、目前出任助教的大衛安察洛堤，領軍踢完餘下的聯賽，以及出戰今夏的世界冠軍球會盃。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬在歐聯8強被阿仙奴淘汰。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e2d03d8245c791524b7700ee1a6dee4/2025-04/2025-04-16T205704Z_1610392217_UP1EL4G1M73EW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬在歐聯8強被阿仙奴淘汰。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖迪比寧咸對於皇馬出局非常失望。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b11ad3e64bba2eca048ff3c29c52ccb4/2025-04/2025-04-16T205435Z_1947864960_UP1EL4G1M2XEM_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖迪比寧咸對於皇馬出局非常失望。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖迪比寧咸(左)對於皇馬出局非常失望。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/95105723f320ef624b7177626a3aa6ef/2025-04/2025-04-16T205425Z_960195032_UP1EL4G1M2OEL_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖迪比寧咸(左)對於皇馬出局非常失望。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬(圖)慘遭阿仙奴淘汰出局。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aab2b4bef62fe6288857cbf9270b7908/2025-04/Spain_Soccer_Champions_League_58177--07521.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬(圖)慘遭阿仙奴淘汰出局。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬中場祖迪比寧咸非常失望。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eafa01eb5aa46710b98c8f564afbcd6a/2025-04/Spain_Soccer_Champions_League_43446--7df5e.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬中場祖迪比寧咸非常失望。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
