        {
            "title": "畀五星先食得？海南餐廳被爆用預製菜 惡老闆仲要撳筷子逼客派like",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"海南餐廳被爆給五星好評才可用餐。大眾點評截圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e3da46e24e53f380187b34d6efe50bb8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041813014720940.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">海南餐廳被爆給五星好評才可用餐。大眾點評截圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近日，有網友反映，海南三亞一餐廳存在服務態度差，菜品疑似提前做好，且須給五星好評才可以就餐等問題。目前，該餐廳被責令停業，三亞市監局正展開調查。\n\n</p><h2>疑預製菜加熱上桌</h2>\n<p>奔流新聞報道，網友在社交平台反映，在海南三亞一家名為「三亞林福記海南風味餐廳」用餐時，拿出團購的二維碼給老闆看，老闆看到是團購「臉直接板起來」，很不情願地驗了券，找了個角落位置給他們坐下，網友發現座位很髒提出換位卻被拒絕。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3426135/\">劏客疑雲︱廬山一餐館「木耳」湯索價¥68 老闆話這材料是關鍵</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當事人發布的菜品圖片。奔流新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e73314022de7104a0d85606918d4445/2025-04/d10306edaaa20a0f13b5d35a33154b1.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當事人發布的菜品圖片。奔流新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"海南餐廳被爆給五星好評才可用餐。大眾點評截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5d29c802ffc206d7c83c0391ba99c8f2/2025-04/ffac996d576c2729ea62e305a839b5d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海南餐廳被爆給五星好評才可用餐。大眾點評截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"海南餐廳被爆給五星好評才可用餐。抖音截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4b0a32806b76e28cf5d653721e7decb/2025-04/c281bd5946d6e357a56a807c805d67e.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海南餐廳被爆給五星好評才可用餐。抖音截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當地市監局通報。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0aa9eae1dee3fda483c6ebecb7f1d00/2025-04/Clipboard24_9.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當地市監局通報。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民留言。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/870cfff3b9b7f18b5de9b9402ab6733e/2025-04/Clipboard25_7.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民留言。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民留言。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/651765b1513a31e908f7785258b245e1/2025-04/Clipboard26_9.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民留言。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-topics/3312880/\">深圳網紅店「笨羅卜」回收剩飯再賣 網民聽完店家解釋更嬲豬</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>隨後店員10分鐘內就上完了菜，網友懷疑是將事先做好的菜加熱端上桌，「也就是10分鐘內同時炒好了螃蟹、蝦、花甲、雞肉、土豆絲、扇貝。」\n\n</p>\n<p>該網友說，準備吃的時候「他（老闆）直接過來按住我們的筷子讓我們給五星級好評，才讓動筷子。」網友品嘗之後感覺菜品味道不好而且量少，蝦還是涼的。\n\n</p>\n<p>該網友還表示，「有兩個女孩子來吃飯，老闆讓兩個女孩子在門口站著等，寧願讓客人在外面站著等也不願讓他們進去坐大桌吃飯，就因為她們是兩個人而且是團購。」\n\n</p>\n<p>對此，三亞市市場監督管理局已聯合三亞市綜合行政執法局立即開展調查，現正在調查中。據悉，該餐廳已被責令停業受查。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
